<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安带着汤姆去了实验室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给汤姆看了一扇小门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上一任魔法师把所有东西都放在这个密室里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>安在密室里四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你需要的药水是能......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，传来了“喵”的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猫咪？”汤姆吃惊地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也发现了密室的门。”猫咪对汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，我找到药水了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆把猫咪说的告诉了安。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把药水混在一起吧。”安说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊？”汤姆看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然我爱我的父亲。”安说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你有一颗善良的心，汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父亲对你和猫咪太不公平了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，皇族们都回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆在王后面前鞠了个躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我非常想念您，王后。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆端上一个杯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为您做了魔法药水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗，汤姆？”王后脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后一口喝下了药水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆屏住了呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会被赶走的！魔法师！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么？”国王大声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都看着王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊......”她张大了嘴巴，但却没有打喷嚏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你治好我了，汤姆！”她开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她摸着猫咪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让猫待在皇宫里吧！”国王大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克生气地走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人都欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>